single op:
  (((`+` 1 2)))
  (((`*` X Y)))
  (((`<` X Y)))
left-to-right within same precedence:
  (((`+` (`+` 1 2) 3)))
  (((`*` (`*` X Y) Z)))
precedence:  +/- < */%:
  (((`+` 1 (`*` 2 3))))
  (((`+` (`*` 1 2) 3)))
comparison:
  (((`><` X Y)))
  (((`<<` X Y)))
  (((`>>` X Y)))
boolean (and/or are infix):
  ((`and` (X) (Y)))
  ((`or` (X) (Y)))
  ((`and` (X) (`or` (Y) (Z))))
bitwise (-+-, -*-, ...):
  (((`-+-` X Y)))
  (((`-*-` X Y)))
